  <brief_title>The Effect of Clonidine in Glycemia During Coronary Artery Bypass Graft With Cardiopulmonary By-pass</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Clonidine in Glycemia During Coronary Artery Bypass Graft With Cardiopulmonary By-pass.</official_title>
